Instagram post by @noorie_rai (verified), 18 January 2018. Photo shows Maa standing on rocks in a stream/waterfall setting. Overlaid text: 'Milte Hai Break Ke Baad' (Meet you after the break), large red text 'INTERVAL', signed 'Noorie'. Bottom-left stamp: '18-01-2018 / 17.08 PM / THURSDAY'. 13 likes. DECODED: Date 18-01-18 encodes to '919' — revealed as the Code of Lord Kalki. Time 17:08 contains '08' = the recurring number 8. The 'INTERVAL' is a deliberate cosmic pause before the transformation journey. Waterfall setting = purification/renewal. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Cosmic Preparation — the Code 919 revealed through the date itself.